Description:
    For selecting mediating effects within exploratory Bayesian mediation
    models (Shi, Shi & Fairchild, 2023, <doi:10.1080/10705511.2022.2164285>).
    Package buzzMed accommodates both continuous and dichotomous outcomes,
    including the dependent variables and the mediators for identifying and
    analyzing mediation pathways.
